Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春天里喝甜茶最舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothin' better than sweet tea in springtime
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's SpongeBob now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我直接进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let myself in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hope you don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛一副苦瓜脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your tree
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no idea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这棵老橡树现在应该是花开正旺才对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This old oak should be in full bloom right now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不应该跟垂柳一样垂泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not weepin' like a willow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.58,0:01:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没有原子橡果射线枪什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you have some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,atomic acorn ray or something?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  帮我操作我的核动力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, help me with my nuclear-powered
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全自动树皮电击枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bark-o-matic zapatron
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得反而更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That just made it worse
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认识一个园艺大师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know someone who's great at gardening
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维生素
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vitamins?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你又成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you've done it again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是一朵奇葩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another fleur de force
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我需要你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的树出毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with my tree
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你们一点都不尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see you don't have any respect
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们优雅的花儿朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for our fine floral friends
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我扯进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Count me out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只打理自己的花园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tend my own garden
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听说你可是全裤头村最厉害的园艺家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard you're the greatest gardener in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且所有植物都喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that all plants love you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll do it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On one condition, that is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,1000,0,,不准质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,1000,0,,No one questions
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,1000,0,,或者打断我的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,1000,0,,or interrupts my process
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,1000,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,1000,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们对树做了测量评估
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we tested my tree to gauge its--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say no more
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己就能诊断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can diagnose it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点橡树味  怪怪的坚果味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Notes of oak, a bit nutty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一丝丝悲苦味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a hint of distress
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有脉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No pulse
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我担心的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just as I feared
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这棵树得了树皮树枝病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tree has bark and branch disease
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听说过那种病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't never heard of that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心  珊迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Miss Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥是咱这最厉害的师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's the best we've got
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.13,0:04:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fertilizer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜有机肥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh manure
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔着头盔咋闻到味的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did he smell through the helmet?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,矿泉水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mineral water
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剪子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shears
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简简单单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我预想的还要严重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is more serious than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  拿这么多风铃跟护符来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what in tarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are all these chimes and charms for?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来试试替代园艺法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are going to try a little alternative gardening
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.11,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 替代园艺法：改自替代疗法\N指在西医之外、缺乏科学根据的疗法 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是流程的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the process
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要引导这棵树正念冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to guide the tree in mindful meditation
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要想象它成长的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to visualize its growth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1574,378)}章鱼哥金曲
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受树根
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel the roots of the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着我念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的树皮很强壮  我的树枝很粗壮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bark is strong, my branches thick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的花蕾很茂盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My buds are bountiful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的耳朵很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ears are bleeding
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的屁股很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My butt is beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点小插曲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A minor hiccup
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust the process
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这流程  到底还要做多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just how much longer is this "process" going to take?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  这可得看树的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Sandy, that's up to the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.30,0:06:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程没完  我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll stay here as long as it takes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能要好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It could be days
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚至好几周
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几周吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weeks, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真够久的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't that somethin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这棵树得补充树液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tree needs sap
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ASAP
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是流程的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Part of the process
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是为了树好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's for the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是流程的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Part of the process
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The process
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,经过很多部分流程后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他又在大半夜来搞园艺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's night gardening again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The process
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The process
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The process
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够这个破流程了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had it with his consarned "process"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够你动不动就来打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had it with your constant interruptions
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来烦我搞好流程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to leave me to my process
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会向他们证明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show them
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,证明给他们所有人看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show them all
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥失败得也够久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's failed for long enough
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿你能帮我劝他离开  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, you can help me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,convince him to leave, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tree
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥做到了不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward really did the impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-are these
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's paintings?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以前是  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They were, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但现在都被我剪下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I cut them up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不只把树给治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't just fix the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还让它更加美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I turned it into something better
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更加壮观了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something sublime
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我不仅是裤头村最厉害的园艺家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm not only the greatest gardener in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.58,0:09:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是全世界最厉害的艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the greatest artist in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下可好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的树还病着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tree is still sick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥现在又在发癫傻乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now Squidward's actin' like a dang ninny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜没法直接问问树出了什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad we can't just ask the tree what's wrong with it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接问树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask the tree?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我正好有道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I think I have just the doodad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的跨物种翻译机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My inter-species translator
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没在植物身上用过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never tried it on plant life
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Testing, testing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Woo doggy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉到有个黏滑的东西在我身上爬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can feel something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rather slimy crawling around me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.25,0:10:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用理他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him none
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过既然我们能聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now that we can chat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问下是什么害你病得树枝一直掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what seems to be bringin' your branches down?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我并没有病  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not suffering from an illness, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个很重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something quite heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连续几天都压住了我的根
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been crushing my roots for days now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是星期天兜完风把车忘在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must'a left her there after my Sunday drive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is much better
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于可以摆脱这些垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally be rid of all this rubbish
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜了你的画  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about your paintings, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我白白毁掉了我的画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I destroyed my paintings for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你毁了画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You destroyed your paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却换来了友情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for friendship
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还是白白毁掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have the nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必担心  亲爱的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fret not, dear Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正因为你有这份关怀的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The way you care
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能成为裤头村最厉害的园艺家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,makes you the greatest gardener in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, that's
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.71,0:11:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是我听过最贴心的一句好话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the nicest thing anyone has ever said to me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想送你一份薄礼  以示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give you a small token of my gratitude
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.02,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp40\c&H00FFC1&}蟹老板\N{\fs30} \N{\fs175}生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(752,430)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,722)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:55.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(636,484)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(800,700)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(740,548)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(596,560)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(640,598)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,366)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道明天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what day tomorrow is?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,距离死亡又接近了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day closer to death?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要我给你个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How 'bout I give you a hint?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Krabs' birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要送他什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we get him?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个不准  我再重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two are not, I repeat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准给我买生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not to be getting me a birthday present
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们送我的每个礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every single one you've gotten me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是彻头彻尾的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been a total disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些都是海绵宝宝一个人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those were all from SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及不准送礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no presents
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以要给他送什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what should we get him?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准送礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No presents
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他那是口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't mean it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真的很想要礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He really wants one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他那是在利用逆反心理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's using reverse psychology
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你这脑子都长反了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're using reverse brains
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别把我扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Count me out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流百货会营业到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Upturn's Department Store is open late
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给他找个好礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get him something nice
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就说是我们两个一起送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll say it's from the both of us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板生日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板生日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们两个一起送的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's from the both of us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们两个一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The both of us?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好跟过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd better go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.18,0:13:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,省得他又买到什么笨玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make sure he doesn't get something stupid again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,446)}上流百货
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要给他买巧克力直升飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should we get him a chocolate helicopter?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是喷气背包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or a jet pack?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳跳糖豆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumping jellybeans?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.28,0:14:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险宠物区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dangerous Pets Department
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,416)}危险宠物
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都爱需要承担责任的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves the gift of responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That thing's dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个小可爱才不危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not this widdle cutie-pie
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He likes you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个倒可能会危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now this one can be dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星哪里危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so dangerous about Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:02.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(868,332)}情怀区
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情怀区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Sentimental Department?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里卖的都是能动情的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where they sell emotional objects
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像是这些照片  拍的都是慈祥老母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like these photos of kindly old mothers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她让我想起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She reminds me of
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:17.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1666,332)}情书
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情书还有促销哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a sale on love letters
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,致我亲爱的翻车鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"My darling Sunfish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多么渴望凝视你鳃上的细丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how I long to gaze upon the filaments of your gills
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的小孔雀鱼献上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From your little guppy"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's so
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好优美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就给蟹老板送那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get that for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  必须得触动他的情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No It has to be something sentimental
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要对他有特殊意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and personal to him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特殊意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Personal?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.21,0:15:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泰迪熊说  蟹老板家里可以找到线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teddy Bear says you'll find a clue in Mr. Krabs' house
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泰迪熊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teddy Bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's what I said
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一吵醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if he wakes up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他发现我们在他家咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and finds us in his house?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跟珍珍晚上向来睡得很死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He and Pearl are heavy sleepers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音再大都吵不醒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loud noises never wake them up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in that case
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从那边进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go in that way
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爬这扇刚好没关的窗户进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll climb in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through this conveniently open window
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到什么了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You find anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说  我也没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said, "Me neither"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this photo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板开蟹堡王之前的旧餐车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Krabs' old food cart before he had The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他以前经常把它停在酷乐湖海滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He used to park it on the beach at Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.30,0:17:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送他这个当情怀礼物刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would make the perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sentimental birthday gift for him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure would
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道那个禁止游泳标志在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know right where that no swimming sign is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.28,0:17:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.82,0:17:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.15,0:17:32.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:32.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a mess
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是我的不安蟹爪综合征又发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Musta been me restless claw syndrome again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,772)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没理由相信他的旧餐车会在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to believe that his old cart would be
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great work, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You found it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be dipped in batter
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们来把它摆正  推去蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get it upright and wheel it to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burglars
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢匪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robbers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想偷我老斯纳格的家  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trying to steal Old Snug's home, are ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寄居蟹可是也有住宅权的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hermit crabs have housing rights too, you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  这位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mister, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.20,0:18:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳格先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snug?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们以为这辆车没人要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We thought this cart was abandoned
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样的  它以前是我们老板的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, it used to belong to our boss
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们觉得可以给他个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we thought we'd surprise him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送他这个当生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by giving it to him on his birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是个情怀礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, a sentimental gift
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情怀是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sentimental, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可拒绝不了情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a sucker for sentiment
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.06,0:18:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给我找样东西当家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,find me another thing I could use as a home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就把这辆旧车给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll give you this old cart
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trashcan?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公共厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Porta Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.07,0:19:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Refrigerator?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我一直想要什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what I always wanted?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要拿船来当家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A boat for a house
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用太高档
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not anything fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.04,0:19:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一艘简陋的小船就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A small, humble boat would do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们照办  就能成交
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do that and you've got a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整晚没睡  净打扫我卧室了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up all night cleaning me room
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破生日提醒我已经上年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lousy birthday reminding me I'm an old krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.19,0:19:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ambush
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.19,0:19:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sneak attack
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打了就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit and run
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们两个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我以前的蟹堡餐车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me old Krabby Kart?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我想的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.00,0:19:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很久以前就把这辆车落在了酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left this cart at Goo Lagoon a long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I hated it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵宝宝想的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all SpongeBob's idea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.51,0:20:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个垃圾让我想起了从前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This piece of junk reminds me of the old days
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时候我完全没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I had no money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No money?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难怪你会讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder you hate it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的收银船哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's me register boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拿它来换你的旧车了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We traded it for your old cart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个装着我钱的收银机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where's the cash register filled with me money?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有可能还在船上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's probably still in the boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个把我船和收银机搞回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two get me boat and register back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有钱也要搞回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all me money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就把你们大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll rip youse limb from limb
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再组装成现代艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and reassemble youse into modern art
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,斯纳格先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Snug?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得把船要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need this boat back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是收银机还在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the cash register is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The money's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  斯纳格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Snug
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the money?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都在我背上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on my back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把钱全花来买这个明朝花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used it all to buy this Imperial Ming vase
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当作我的新家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as my new home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toodles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.65,0:21:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么看待现代艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about modern art?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得它摈弃了历史风格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I find its rejection of historical styles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be quite refreshing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收银机里面的钱要不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get your money back from the register
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛这么高兴  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why so happy, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐车去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where's the cart?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个客人把它当作收藏品了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer recognized it as a collector's item
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给的钱远远超过了它的实际价值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He paid me way more than it was worth
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天简直是最棒的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best birthday ever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然这都是我想的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was all my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.69,0:22:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然我也得扣你未来的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And of course, I'll have to dock your future pay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垫我收银机里的钱  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the contents of me register, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.74,0:22:31.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:31.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今天来休假
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're taking a day off
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要去博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a museum?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得现代艺术摈弃了历史风格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I find modern art's rejection of historical styles
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我耳目一新  你说是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,quite refreshing, don't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完全同意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I completely agree
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.88,0:22:45.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:45.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,typical
